Leadership in Investment Technology
Milestone Group is in the investment automation business.  We serve fund managers, specialist investment managers such as OCIO’s, retirement savings providers and administrators of pooled investments. Designed for low operating cost, high extensibility and improved product management, our pControl enterprise investment automation platform leads the global funds industry in automation efficiency, cost of ownership and improved risk control.










